1166.name: Dur 6 Mo (Powder alloy F75)
1166.Applications: PTA and or laser overlay welding on wear parts that need to outlast new parts where high temperatures combined with corrosion and wear resistance is required. 3D printing of parts for medical applications as prostatic implants such as replacement hips and knee condyles.
1166.Suitable_For: Replacement hips, knee parts, condyles, Gas turbine parts, fuel nozzles, orthopedic implants.
